{
  "description": "C 盘白名单目录 - 这些目录绝对不能删除或移动",
  "protectedPaths": [
    "C:\\Windows\\System32",
    "C:\\Windows\\SysWOW64",
    "C:\\Program Files",
    "C:\\Program Files (x86)",
    "C:\\ProgramData",
    "C:\\Users\\*\\Documents",
    "C:\\Users\\*\\Desktop",
    "C:\\Users\\*\\Pictures",
    "C:\\Users\\*\\Videos",
    "C:\\Users\\*\\Music",
    "C:\\Users\\*\\Downloads\\*",
    "C:\\Users\\*\\OneDrive"
  ],
  "protectedExtensions": [
    "*.sys",
    "*.dll",
    "*.exe",
    "*.msi"
  ],
  "notes": [
    "System32 和 SysWOW64 是系统核心目录，绝对不能动",
    "Program Files 是程序安装目录，删除会导致程序无法运行",
    "用户文档目录（Documents、Desktop 等）包含个人文件，需要保护",
    "OneDrive 是云同步目录，删除会导致数据丢失"
  ]
}
